############
# Fastmail #
############

IMAPAccount fastmail
# Host mail.messagingengine.com
# Port 992
Host imaps-proxy.messagingengine.com
Port 80
User benswift@fastmail.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.mbsync-fastmail"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Account fastmail

MaildirStore fastmail-local
Path ~/Maildir/personal/
Inbox ~/Maildir/personal/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel fastmail
Master :fastmail-remote:
Slave :fastmail-local:
Patterns "*"
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *

#################
# ANU Office365 #
#################

IMAPAccount anu
Host outlook.office365.com
Port 993
User u2548636@anu.edu.au
PassCmd "cat ~/.mbsync-anu"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

IMAPStore anu-remote
Account anu

MaildirStore anu-local
Path ~/Maildir/anu/
Inbox ~/Maildir/anu/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel anu
Master :anu-remote:
Slave :anu-local:
Patterns "Archive" "Deleted" "Items" "Drafts" "INBOX" "Junk E-Mail" "Notes" "Sent Items"
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *

